{"tid":676730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由馬桶掘70米隧道逃獄 囚犯幾乎成功但窒息死","createTime":"2018-05-24T15:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T04:35:08.000Z","uid":150685,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"713c6e13a88070043c63ef8b5f9cabd61ceb5d00","tid":676730,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180523/large/1527062264_6534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180523%2Flarge%2F1527062264_6534.jpg&h=3ecee2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西一個最高設防監獄發生企圖越獄事件，一名囚犯在自己囚室的馬桶下掘了一條長達70米的隧道，已經延伸至監獄牆壁外，但囚犯卻在洞內感到不適折返囚室，最後卻因缺氧死亡。<br />\n<br />\n出事的「蒙特克里斯托監獄」（Monte Cristo）位於羅賴馬州（Roraima）博阿維斯塔（Boa Vista），是當地最大監獄。26歲殺人犯埃萬熱利斯塔（Judson Cunha Evangelista）相信已花了數月掘隧道。<br />\n<br />\n警方周二在其囚室的馬桶下發現隧道，派出150名警員、共花費7小時才弄清秘道的方向。他們在洞內調查時，發現幾袋泥沙、一條延至地道盡頭的電線，以及一個燈泡，而這條地底秘道長達70米，已經越過了監獄的圍牆及通電圍欄，僅差幾米就可以到達外面森林的地面。<br />\n<br />\n當局相信埃萬熱利斯塔計劃利用地道向其他囚犯收費，協助他們大規模越獄。經警方檢查後，目前有關地道已經用水泥封好。<br />\n<br />\n「蒙特克里斯托監獄」去年1月因兩個幫派的囚犯爆發暴力衝突而發生監獄騷亂，特種部隊奉命出動協助恢復秩序，至少33名囚犯死亡。監獄內環境擠迫，獄中本來最多可囚禁750名囚犯，但事發時監獄內的囚犯人數竟超過1,400人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180524/58226328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58226328&d=XH6AhjTccanxsmHwaXTVENU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bf7ce108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58226328&h=20096847\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180524/58226328</a>"},{"pid":"3cbe3ce49aff81ce58c94f76d91449d1694ee18a","tid":676730,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"「蒙特克里斯托監獄」去年1月因兩個幫派的囚犯爆發暴力衝突而發生監獄騷亂，特種部隊奉命出動協助恢復秩序，至少33名囚犯死亡。監獄內環境擠迫，獄中本來最多可囚禁750名囚犯，但事發時監獄內的囚犯人數竟超過1,400人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地獄鬼國"},{"pid":"c59e50ba34485155b033e5c43f90ed85b57115e6","tid":676730,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"刺激1995"},{"pid":"f140ceca31cc65cfe027a87a5d092a0d2fdb1f4a","tid":676730,"uid":6532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c59e50ba34485155b033e5c43f90ed85b57115e6","tid":676730,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"刺激1995"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"月黑高飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d7a2b164b248ed68d96fc8298c28a8d8c9757e","tid":676730,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"逃百里者，半死九十"},{"pid":"26729d5a892855913efb02032bb8456a6e4a784d","tid":676730,"uid":145779,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"諗起掘鑽石礦張圖 你永遠唔知離終點幾遠 如果佢堅持多幾米係咪唔洗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcc351f111218fa29e95337f8ea6dff588c4ce9","tid":676730,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我睇月黑高飛都有諗過咁做會唔會窒息死，成條屎渠都係沼氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4136459e5b613472edf1b8d4fb9582aa5e6da616","tid":676730,"uid":24989,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"屎路一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d047283336fb2719a27936893022053f4aa7da","tid":676730,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quo